{"tid":1583484,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"曾憲梓都死埋，93 歲既江澤民仲在生","createTime":"2019-09-20T15:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T19:29:41.000Z","uid":1654,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0d0428171db037b47b794dbfdeff6198f6fa32","tid":1583484,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/07/29/realtime/6625572.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F07%2F29%2Frealtime%2F6625572.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=be925f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc44d015e7caaceb0284f67ade9e21672207dc90","tid":1583484,"uid":265221,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:27:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府</span></span>借減碳排放為名，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要向中國買電</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」詻詢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日截止</span></span><br />\n快啲將你既意見SEND EMAIL去：  comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n✏參考意見✏<br />\n<br />\n致可持續發展委員會成員：<br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」諮詢中，當局建議以「 更緊密的區域合作」向中國購買零排放電力，然而本港電力穩定度遠高於中國南方電網，擔心向中國買電會帶來電力不穩，影響本港金融、航運、交通、以至市民日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《巴黎協定》為一些面積小、欠缺天然資源的小島嶼發展中國家(Small Island Developing States,SIDS) 如新加坡、斐濟等，可因應它們特殊情況，制訂關於溫室氣體低排放發展的策略。<br />\n由於香港地少人多，局限可再生能源發展，亦缺乏天然資源，可選擇的減排策略有限，與其他小島嶼發展中國家情況面臨同樣的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n就此本人有以下意見：<br />\n<br />\n一. 聯網供電會損害供電穩定，故此反對進一步向中國買電，反對採取更緊密的區域合作，香港應以本地發電為主，確保電力穩定；<br />\n二. 遵照2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢，增加本地天然氣發電及可再生能源比例，代替區域聯網；<br />\n三. 爭取香港以地區名義，直接向政府間氣候變化專門委員會(IPCC)匯報減排策略；<br />\n四. 爭取以發展中國家/地區(Small Island Developing States) 名義，因應香港的情況，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n五. 放緩人口增長，收緊移民政策，減低整體耗電量；<br />\n六. 制訂具體香港再工業化政策，加強本港農業及回收業的支援，減少貨物入口時的碳排放。"},{"pid":"ef293c8dfb29d8287926b833c3c1a9012f4913bc","tid":1583484,"uid":133279,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞馬哈蒂爾94歲仲做緊首相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1001a186e8d748e156770698db51104e1aa9254a","tid":1583484,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:36:21.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書<br />\n<br />\n有時有D野真係早D走好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597768a3561d5f04eb5f7624f6a6e13e2327ab10","tid":1583484,"uid":59633,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:47:10.000Z","msg":"江澤民長命過亞視"},{"pid":"1accd688b46ff0b1b0825f3121acf355412ade77","ti